  "response": "There are several solar panel installation providers in La Habra, California, that you can consider. Here are a few options to look into:\n\n1. **SunPower by Precis**: They offer high-quality solar panels and professional installation services, and are known for their efficiency and customer service.\n\n2. **Infinity Solar**: A local company with experience in residential solar panel installations. They provide tailored solar solutions and aim for customer satisfaction.\n\n3. **Vivint Solar**: They are known for offering solar panel installations with flexible financing options, and have a nationwide presence including service in La Habra.\n\n4. **SolarMax Technology**: A reputable provider that offers comprehensive solar solutions, including financing options and detailed consultations.\n\n5. **Green Convergence**: They specialize in solar electrical installations and have a strong portfolio in residential solar systems.\n\nIt\u2019s a good idea to get quotes from a few providers, check their reviews and certifications, and consider their offerings and financing options to find the best fit for your needs. You can also look into local customer reviews and ratings on platforms like Yelp, Google Reviews, and SolarReviews to ensure that the provider has a solid reputation.",
